# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your own values.
# `.env.local` is gitignored — never commit real secrets.

# ─── Client (exposed to the browser via Vite) ────────────────────────────────

# start.gg personal access token. Required for loading tournaments from
# start.gg in the Top 8 and Prediction tools.
# Get one at: https://start.gg/admin/profile/developer
VITE_START_GG_TOKEN=

# ─── Server (used by Vercel serverless functions in `api/`) ──────────────────

# Challonge API v1 key. Required only if you're working on Challonge support.
# Get one at: https://challonge.com/settings/developer
CHALLONGE_API_KEY=

# Vercel feature-flags backing value. Optional in local dev — when unset,
# `api/flags.ts` falls back to the defaults defined in the file. New flags
# default to ON in dev (`import.meta.env.DEV`) and OFF in prod.
# FLAGS=
